 mplot <- function(m){m %>%
  tidy(conf.int = TRUE) %>%
    filter(term!="(Intercept)") %>%
ggplot() + 
  aes(x = term,
      y = estimate, 
      ymin = conf.low, 
      ymax = conf.high)+ 
    geom_hline(yintercept = 0, linetype =2) + 
  geom_pointrange() + coord_flip() }

countModel <- glm(reelections ~ corporate + constituent, 
            data = d,  #%>% distinct(), 
            #contrasts = list(interest = contr.sum(2)),
         family = poisson)  

summary(countModel)
